print("""Your future self says 'wonderful.' They disappear as you begin
to go in and out of a daze as flashes of your future flood your mind.
After what seems like hours, you wake back up.
Your future self steps toward you, except this time they seem a little
different. They have a slight glow about them. Your future says
'Let's make sure you are prepared for what is ahead, and that you have
the FAITH in yourself to achieve everything you set out to do.

I am going to give you a series of phrases which will help you
develop the confidence to achieve your BURNING DESIRE.

Repeat them 5 times each after me.""")

print("""First. I know that I have the ability to achieve the object of
my Definite Purpose in life, therefore, I DEMAND of myself persistent,
continuous action toward its attainment, and I here and now promise to render
such action.""")
faith_formula()
print(seps)

print("""Second. I realize the dominating thoughts of my mind will eventually
reproduce themselves in outward, physical action, and gradually transform
themselves into physical reality, therefore, I will concentrate my thoughts for
thirty minutes daily, upon the task of thinking of the person I intend to
become, thereby creating in my mind a clear mental picture of that person.""")
faith_formula()
print(seps)

print("""Third. I know through the principle of auto-suggestion, any desire
that I persistently hold in my mind will eventually seek expression through
some practical means of attaining the object back of it, therefore, I will
devote ten minutes daily to demanding of myself the development of
SELF-CONFIDENCE.""")
faith_formula()
print(seps)

print("""Fourth. I have clearly written down a description of my
DEFINITE CHIEF AIM in life, and I will never stop trying, until I shall have
